name: Basic Women Wear
one_liner: While feminine and refined, Oscalito’s Basic Collection for women focuses on the timeless essential.
description: “Quality”, “attention to detail” and “excellence in raw materials” are our watchwords.The purest silk, extra-fine Australian merino wool, mercerised cotton, micromodal. These precious fibres are what makes the Basic Collection unique.A reliable friend year-round: Oscalito’s Basic Collection.
